query:
SELECT 
  m.moduleNumber,
  m.title as module_title,
  COUNT(a.id) as question_count,
  SUM(CASE WHEN a.questionText LIKE '%PLACEHOLDER%' OR a.questionText LIKE '%placeholder%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as placeholder_count,
  CASE 
    WHEN SUM(CASE WHEN a.questionText LIKE '%PLACEHOLDER%' OR a.questionText LIKE '%placeholder%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) > 0 THEN 'HAS PLACEHOLDERS'
    WHEN COUNT(a.id) = 0 THEN 'NO QUESTIONS'
    ELSE 'COMPLETE'
  END as assessment_status
FROM modules m
LEFT JOIN assessments a ON m.id = a.moduleId
GROUP BY m.id, m.moduleNumber, m.title
ORDER BY m.moduleNumber
